['text':' Tests the behaviour of the $merge stage with whenMatched=merge and whenNotMatched=fail.','line_number':1,'multiline':False]['text':'','line_number':2,'multiline':False]['text':' Cannot implicitly shard accessed collections because a collection can be implictly created and','line_number':3,'multiline':False]['text':' exists when none is expected.','line_number':4,'multiline':False]['text':' Test $merge when some documents in the source collection don't have a matching document in','line_number':17,'multiline':False]['text':' the target collection.','line_number':18,'multiline':False]['text':' Single document without a match.','line_number':20,'multiline':False]['text':' Since there is no way to guarantee the ordering of the writes performed by $merge, it','line_number':25,'multiline':False]['text':' follows that the contents of the target collection will depend on when the write which','line_number':26,'multiline':False]['text':' triggers the MergeStageNoMatchingDocument error executes. As such, we test that the','line_number':27,'multiline':False]['text':' target collection contains some combination of its original documents and expected','line_number':28,'multiline':False]['text':' updates. In particular, it should be the case that each document has fields '_id' and','line_number':29,'multiline':False]['text':' 'b', but may or not have field 'a'. All present fields must share the same value as _id.','line_number':30,'multiline':False]['text':' Multiple documents without a match.','line_number':48,'multiline':False]['text':' Test $merge when all documents in the source collection have a matching document in the','line_number':58,'multiline':False]['text':' target collection.','line_number':59,'multiline':False]['text':' Source has a single element with a match in the target.','line_number':61,'multiline':False]['text':' Source has multiple documents with matches in the target.','line_number':70,'multiline':False]['text':' Test $merge when the source collection is empty. The target collection should not be','line_number':81,'multiline':False]['text':' modified.','line_number':82,'multiline':False]['text':' Test $merge uses unorderded batch update. When a mismatch is detected in a batch, the error','line_number':91,'multiline':False]['text':' should be returned once the batch is processed and no further documents should be processed','line_number':92,'multiline':False]['text':' and updated.','line_number':93,'multiline':False]['text':' 16MB','line_number':95,'multiline':False]['text':' Each document is just under 1MB in order to allow for some extra space for writes that need','line_number':97,'multiline':False]['text':' to be serialized over the wire in certain cluster configurations. Otherwise, the number of','line_number':98,'multiline':False]['text':' modified/unmodified documents would be off by one depending on how our cluster is configured.','line_number':99,'multiline':False]['text':' Insert 'numDocs' documents of size 'docSize' into the source collection.','line_number':106,'multiline':False]['text':' Copy over documents from the source collection into the target and remove the 'padding'','line_number':109,'multiline':False]['text':' field from the projection, so we can distinguish which documents have been modified by','line_number':110,'multiline':False]['text':' the $merge stage.','line_number':111,'multiline':False]['text':' Remove one document from the target collection so that $merge fails. This document should','line_number':115,'multiline':False]['text':' be in the first batch of the aggregation pipeline below, which sorts documents by the _id','line_number':116,'multiline':False]['text':' field in ascending order. Since each document in the source collection is 1MB, and the','line_number':117,'multiline':False]['text':' max batch size is 16MB, the first batch will contain documents with the _id in the range','line_number':118,'multiline':False]['text':' of [0, 15].','line_number':119,'multiline':False]['text':' Ensure the target collection has 'numDocs' - 1 documents without the 'padding' field.','line_number':122,'multiline':False]['text':' Run the $merge pipeline and ensure it fails, as there is one document in the source','line_number':125,'multiline':False]['text':' collection without a match in the target.','line_number':126,'multiline':False]['text':' There will be maxDocsInBatch documents in the batch, one without a match.','line_number':130,'multiline':False]['text':' All remaining documents except those in the first batch must be left unmodified.','line_number':132,'multiline':False]